+------+-------+--------------------+
| id   | c2    | normal(1,2,c2)     |
+------+-------+--------------------+
|    1 |     0 | 1.2038371110290758 |
|    1 |     0 | 1.2038371110290758 |
|    1 |     0 | 1.2038371110290758 |
|    2 |  NULL |               NULL |
|    2 |  NULL |               NULL |
|    2 |  NULL |               NULL |
|    3 | 32767 | 0.8383822255959938 |
|    3 | 32767 | 0.8383822255959938 |
|    3 | 32767 | 0.8383822255959938 |
+------+-------+--------------------+
